[SPEAKER_01] ovaj za Daruvara,

493
00:47:17,840 --> 00:47:19,900
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam, ovaj gore za Vočin,

494
00:47:19,900 --> 00:47:20,980
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj za pakrac.

495
00:47:20,980 --> 00:47:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] Sada ih ne nabrajem imenima,

496
00:47:23,900 --> 00:47:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali mogao bi nabrojati imenima.

497
00:47:26,539 --> 00:47:28,860
[SPEAKER_00] Vlado, jesi ikad pomislio da je uzavut?

498
00:47:28,860 --> 00:47:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ne.

499
00:47:29,960 --> 00:47:30,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo što ti radiš.

500
00:47:30,820 --> 00:47:35,119
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja ne bradio to da smatram da je to uzavut.

501
00:47:35,119 --> 00:47:35,139
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja ne bradio to da smatram da je to uzavut.

502
00:47:35,139 --> 00:47:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam malo htio isprovocirati.

503
00:47:37,719 --> 00:47:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kad vidiš sve da,

504
00:47:39,420 --> 00:47:42,159
[SPEAKER_00] kad vidiš sve crno na bijelo,

505
00:47:42,159 --> 00:47:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] pa opet treba istina se znat.

506
00:47:46,360 --> 00:47:46,940
[SPEAKER_00] Da, da, da.

507
00:47:46,940 --> 00:47:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] Velim, ja sam namenu sad ovo malo isprovocirati.

508
00:47:49,500 --> 00:47:51,500
