509
00:47:51,500 --> 00:47:52,280
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, mora se znat.

510
00:47:52,280 --> 00:47:54,219
[SPEAKER_01] Tako, ali nek se zna istina.

511
00:47:54,219 --> 00:47:54,400
