[SPEAKER_01] i šta ćeš ti onda?

585
00:50:50,659 --> 00:50:53,139
[SPEAKER_00] Kažem, klasično ne može se naručit,

586
00:50:53,139 --> 00:50:54,519
[SPEAKER_00] što je isto ono,

587
00:50:54,519 --> 00:50:57,699
[SPEAKER_00] humano i vidi se veličina tvojeg rada i...

588
00:50:57,699 --> 00:50:58,280
[SPEAKER_01] No vidite,

