00:51:50,800 --> 00:51:55,199
[SPEAKER_00] Lado, a što bi ti, ovako, pred kraj smo poručio obiteljima koji još...

616
00:51:55,199 --> 00:51:57,199
[SPEAKER_00] čekaju, koje...

617
00:51:57,199 --> 00:52:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] koje još uvijek čekaju pravdu.

618
00:52:00,460 --> 00:52:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, da tako kažem.

619
00:52:03,000 --> 00:52:07,099
[SPEAKER_00] Teško, da, komprašati.

620
00:52:07,099 --> 00:52:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] Teško, reko se...

621
00:52:08,360 --> 00:52:09,960
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ovo što sam ja čuo, evo,

622
00:52:09,960 --> 00:52:13,639
